(488, 'Twin Bridge Marina', '11071 Josh Green Ln, Ste 100, Mount Vernon, WA 98273', 'Mount Vernon', 'WA', '98273', '(360) 466-1443', 'http://www.twinbridgesmarina.com/', '', 'Marinas Services', 'Automotive', 'SpecialtiesTwin Bridges Marina is the first full service indoor heated dry stack marina in the state of Washington. Simply put, our goal is to provide our customers the best location, convenience and value for their recreational boating experience. Beyond the security and amenities offered by a heated dry-stack marina, Twin Bridges takes pride in impeccable customer service and the desire to know you personally.HistoryEstablished in 2001.Twin Bridges Marina opened for business in June, 2001 as the first full service indoor heated dry stack marina in the State of Washington.', 'Mon-Sun 9:00 am - 5:00 pm'),
