(850, 'Kammerman\'s Marina', '447 Carson Avenue, Atlantic City, NJ 08401', 'Atlantic City', 'NJ', '8401', '(609) 348-8418', 'https://www.kammermansmarina.com/', '', 'Marinas Services', 'Automotive', 'SpecialtiesKammerman\'s Marina is the largest and busiest boat fueling station in AC - New Jersey\'s quickest & easiest access from the ocean & ICW for fuel and transient dockage.Family owned and operated since 1961, Kammerman\'s Marina has been serving the finest captains for 55 years. We offer competitive fuel prices, bulk fuel pricing, transient & seasonal dockage, free WIFI marine mechanics on call, bait, water supply, restrooms, showers, pump out, electric, laundry facilities, a ship\'s store, and a helpful staff. Kammerman\'s will ensure you are prepared to make the very best of your voyage.HistoryEstablished in 1961.The business has been family-owned and operated for more than 55 year.', 'Mon-Sun 7:00 am - 7:00 pm'),
