g on achieving the best possible outcome for her patients.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3><strong>2. Dr. Raffaella Armstrong</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Dr. Raffaella Armstrong is one of Miami\'s most experienced cosmetic dentists. In 1994, she graduated from the University of Kentucky College of Dentistry. Dr. Raffaella then attended an advanced education program in Italy before earning a dental degree from the \"European Community\". He has received extensive training in Cosmetic Dentistry and Complete Dental Rehabilitation. She combines the most common methods with the most innovative technologies to provide safe, effective, and affordable care. Her dental practice is focused on restoring and enhancing your smile\'s natural beauty. The clinic uses conservative, state-of-the-art procedures that result in beautiful, long-lasting smiles.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3><strong>3. Dr. Ramon Bana</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Dr. Ramon Bana completed his medical training at Marquette University. He also attended Florida International University for his undergraduate degree. He maintains the highest standards in dentistry by utilizing the most recent techniques and offering his patients the latest technology. The dental clinic combines the latest technology with the finest cosmetic products to help patients achieve beautiful and lasting results.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3><strong>Best Cosmetic Dentist In California</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Here are some best and most popular cosmetic dentists in California:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3><strong>1. Dr. Emil Hawary</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Dr. Emil Haw